para_trans: Majalgaon, District Beed 60 as a special case
Regarding the sanction of a women's hospital with beds.
Government Decision No: Establishment-2024 / No.88 / Health-4
Read: - Letter No. of Joint Director, Healthcare Hospitals, Mumbai: By J. No. / Room 3 / T-7 / Female
Hospital Majalgaon / Beed 60. Sl. M / J. No. 2636-38/24 Date 26.2.2024.
Proposal: - The Government is considering sanctioning a 60-bed Women's Hospital at Majalgaon, District Beed.
The following decisions are being taken in this regard.
Approval for grant of 60-bed Women's Hospital at Majalgaon, District Beed as a Special Case
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
